How do js codes get executed?

Machine >> Binary code (0, 1);

Excution context(environment name)
    1) parser(compiler) : code check (compilation error)
    2) interpreter: transform (Ram htl thein) (human lan => Binary code) a = 01000001 = 65
    3) VM => Code execute => response (runtime error)